  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f6a24499ac4184dc79a002cdfe2c07a7, type: 3}
  m_Name: OffMapDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  isConversation: 0
  speakerName:
  - Marcus
  paragraphs:
  - Wow. real mature dude.
  - We've worked so hard on this game, and its in beta. We made this super cohesive
    narrative, made all the components work together, all for you to play!
  - But no. You HAD to go ahead and just walk off the map in the first 30 seconds
    of the game.
  - I hope you're happy with yourself. There's literally nothing down here. All there
    is left to do is just reset the game and play it for real this time.
  - Unless your thing is jumping off the map into the void, in which I guess you
    could play this as some sort of skydiver simulator, but that is such a waste
    of this game.
  - ...Unless your thing is jumping off the map into the void over and over, in which
    I guess you could play this as some sort of skydiver simulator, but that is such
    a waste of this game.
  - Anyways, real mature dude. seriously.
